」。他说，这些新的限制是遏制这些紧迫问题的重要措施。他没有透露谁在抓取推特的数据，也没有说明这个问题持续了多长时间和详细解释系统如何被操纵。推特限制每日浏览数量，马斯克称数据被「极端抓取、系统操纵」_ 未来 2%_ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-08d7ecd78c9514a789b9fbd6221c74c7_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609947405"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI3Iitpc+2qIQ/EAMaCDk3ODI0NDY5INK/haUGMAA43QFAKHIJNjA5OTQ3NDA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1688357430.88963", "card_id": "Q_332509582", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 62}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三国演义里有哪些很坑的谋士？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7e557f4c71100b5c9cd4431a461e31c6_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/332509582"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3Iitpc+2qIQ/EAMaCDM2MTY4MDY5IPOl4egFMAA4vgFAKXIJMzMyNTA5NTgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1688357430.89493", "card_id": "Q_608837406", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "售价 33.5 万元，坦克 500 Hi4-T 值得入手吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "关注了这台车很久了，现在插混版终于出来了，33.5 万，大家觉得这个价格可以冲吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1eeb526018fe298bda43292122707805_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/608837406"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3Iitpc+2qIQ/EAMaCDk3NTc3ODIxINTE5qQGMAA4tw